SQL_STMT_U.val: Select cast(sum(CDEP_ACTUALAMOUNTCLNT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CDEP_ACTUALAMOUNTHELL) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CDEP where CDEP_ADMNO = :2 and CDEP_CLNTNO = :3 and CDEP_TYPE = 4 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows

SELECT
CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASTOCK) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2))
FROM :1/ACCC
WHERE ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 AND ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 AND ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' AND ACCC_MUTTYPE = :5
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SELECT STCY_CURRENCY, STCY_TOTADEBTNOTESMENTIONED, STCY_TOTACREDNOTESMENTIONED FROM :1/SCHT, :1/STCY WHERE SCHT_ADMNO = :2 AND SCHT_CLNTNO =:3 AND SCHT_BOOKED <> 'Y' AND STCY_SCHT_NO = SCHT_NO FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

Text.val: SUM ( Pend. Inv. Recalculated STCY_CURRENCY > CLNT108_ACC_CURR )

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CAST( SUM(BTCP_AMOUNTCURRH) AS DECIMAL(13,2)) FROM :1/BTCP WHERE BTCP_ADMNO_INITIAL = :2 AND BTCP_CLNTNO_INITIAL = :3 AND BTCP_STATUS <2 FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

Text.val: SUM ( Pending Payments from BTCP. Recalculated to CLNT108_ACC_CURR)
